- Created a CRUD application using Spring Boot framework and interacted with Rest API, Lombok, Java Persistence API, H2 and MySQL Databases.
- Used JPA's abstract functions and SQL native code to build business logic and tested various endpoints using Postman.
- Focused on Inversion of Control and avoided using concrete implementations
- Added logging, error management and performed unit tests for Controller, Service and Repository layers using Junit and Mockito
- Added Springboot profiles to add configuration for different application environments
- Created custom actuator endpoints and managed default actuator endpoints
